Package com.ctb.bean.request

Class Summary
FilterParams Contains a list of FilterParam objects, which are applied to the data set returned by a platform call to produce a filtered result list.
FilterParams.FilterParam Represents an individual filter to be applied to a list of results from a platform call
FilterParams.FilterType Contains the available filter types, to use, attach one of the static internal filter types to a FilterParam object
PageParams Contains paging parameters, which are applied to the data set returned by a platform call to produce a single page of a result list
SortParams Contains a list of SortParam objects, which are applied to the data set returned by a platform call to produce a sorted result list.
SortParams.SortParam Represents an individual sort to be applied to a list of results from a platform call
SortParams.SortType Contains the available sort types, to use, attach one of the static internal sort types to a SortParam object
